&#8220;luxurious&#8221; and &#8220;comfortable&#8221; categories, aimed at high- and middle-income groups. Zayat and 
Ricciardi, &#8220;El derecho a la defensa ...&#8221; (footnote 7 above), pp. 3&#8211;4. 
</p>
<p> 
</p>
<p>9
