</p>
<p>was established in 1991 to &#8220;promote measures to achieve the land-title regularization of publicly 
owned land by its transfer to its occupants&#8221;. This programme was replaced in 2008 by the National 
Social Land Commission under Decree No. 341/2008. 
</p>
<p> 
