that treats all inhabitants fairly and makes it possible to move away from a policy based on preference 
and arbitrariness&#8221;. ACIJ and COHRE, &#8220;El IVC ...&#8221; (footnote 42, above), p. 21. 
</p>
<p> 
</p>
<p>51
 See, inter alia, Ombudsman&#8217;s Office of the Autonomous City of Buenos Aires, &#8220;Los desalojos y la 
</p>
<p>emergencia habitacional ...&#8221; (footnote 44 above); Universidad Nacional de General Sarmiento, 
Instituto del Conurbano, Info-Habitat Metropolitano, Movimiento por la Reforma Urbana en la 
Argentina and COHRE, &#8220;Conclusiones del seminario ...&#8221; (footnote 35 above); CELS, &#8220;D&#233;ficit 
